Invocation Name: lime out
des:
LymeOutLive brings you the very best in feelgood music and programming. With a focus on mental health, wellness and community, LymeOutLive blends talk shows featuring inspiring guests sharing their stories and experiences, with great entertainment. 

Join Alban Griffith and his team for regular live broadcasts include The Feelgood Music Show, The Mental Health Show and Let's Talk, as well as a Saturday programme dedicated to Grenadian Culture and Music, and the Sunday Gospel Show. 

There's something for everyone, with new shows and programmes being added regularly and 24 hour music ranging from 80's pop, 90's RnB, reggae, slow jams and all the old school classics to bring the feelgood feeling.

Find out all the latest on www.lymeoutlive.com and follow us on Lymeoutlive on Facebook to stay up to date.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
